data.description: Discover a charming townhome in the heart of Boynton Beach! This property offers a spacious layout with 3 bedrooms, 2 newly renovated bathrooms, and a beautifully renovated kitchen. Includes a mental roof, perfect for protection against Florida storms and hurricanes.  It is located in a desirable area, close to the Boynton Beach Mall, Turnpike, and I-95. In addition, the property is situated conveniently near top rated schools including Citrus Cove Elementary and Boynton High. This residence boasts a serene atmosphere with a covered front patio for relaxation in a quiet neighborhood. Community offers several amenities such as a clubhouse, pool, basketball, and tennis court. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own in one of Boynton Beach's sought-after neighborhoods!
